<p>Hi! I’m <span class="fn" title="Hugo Roy">Hugo</span>. I’m an
attorney in Paris (but this is my personal space).  <span
class="p-note">I am a former Vice-President of <a href="//fdn.fr"
style="display:inline-block"><img alt=""
src="//www.fdn.fr/wp-content/uploads/logo-fdn.png" height="19"> <span
class="org" title="FDN">French Data Network</span></a> (France’s
oldest Internet access provider), where I co-started the <a
href="//exegetes.eu.org/">Exégètes Amateurs</a> (a digital rights
litigation group). I also cofounded <a href="//tosdr.org"
style="display:inline-block"><img alt=""
src="//tosdr.org/img/tosdr-icon-19.png"> <span class="org"
title="ToSDR">Terms of Service; Didn't Read</span></a> and I sit on
the board of the <a href="//www.fsfe.org"
style="display:inline-block"><img alt=""
src="//fsfe.org/graphics/stars-smaller.png" height="19"> <span
class="org">Free Software Foundation Europe</span></a>. True
Zappaist.</span> </p>

